{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cff11f9cfd","title":"在中共中央政治局会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f93bbc9093","index":0,"year":1943,"month":12,"day":1,"articleId":"cff11f9cfd"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"46bf3c0249","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央政治局会议上的讲话”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"cff11f9cfd"},{"id":"302edb1ec9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年12月1日）我们现在的纲领很简单，就是无产阶级领导的人民大众的反帝反封建的革命，一切政治、经济、军事、文化都是如此。这里面有人民大众与帝国主义封建主义的斗争，人民大众很多，首先是几方万农民，其次是几千万小资产阶级，在反帝反封建斗争中资产阶级也参加，抗日时期地主也参加，但必须在无产阶级领导之下。许多同志如王明同志就不了解这一点[1]这是毛泽东在中共中央政治局会议上讲话的一部分。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"cff11f9cfd"}],"page":{"id":"947fb4c907","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"cff11f9cfd","start":253,"end":253}}}},"__N_SSG":true}